                                            in the absence of other clinical signs and symptoms.<br>
                                            <b>Prolonged use:</b> Tolerance, tachyphylaxis, and dose-related
                                            increases in adverse events have been reported with use beyond 24
                                            hours.<br> Withdrawal: Withdrawal symptoms (eg, nausea, vomiting,
                                            agitation,
